team.floracore.common.config

类 ConfigKeys

  • java.lang.Object
    • team.floracore.common.config.ConfigKeys

  • public class ConfigKeys
extends java.lang.Object
    All of the ConfigKeys used by FloraCore.

    The getKeys() method and associated behaviour allows this class to function a bit like an enum, but with generics.
